<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Spotlight on...Kevin Costner (``The Postman'')
 &HT;    By Steve Murray
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``No Way Out'': Costner is a CIA liaison framed for the murder
of Sean Young in this remake of ``The Big Clock.''
