<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-24 19:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5246 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-WORLDCUP-SPAIN-NY     06-24 0803
