<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-24 19:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5317 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KIDNAP-FAGAN-BOS &LR;      06-24 0785
