 Wednesday, June 24, 1998     
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed and will file these stories
for Thursday. If you have questions, please call Susie McBee or Tim
Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about Houston Chronicle
sports stories, please call the Houston Chronicle Sports
Department, 713-220-7896.
</P>
