bunch of questions that ought to be asked.''
</P>
<P>
   Bentsen said he was ``somewhat perturbed that the Navy has just
dropped this in everybody's lap like it's no big deal,'' noting
that napalm is a mixture of gasoline, highly toxic benzene and
polystyrene.
</P>
<P>
   ``We need to be concerned about the movement of it, and the
public needs to be adequately notified about it,'' Bentsen said.
</P>
<P>
   In addition to contacting the governor and congressional
delegation, GNI notified, the mayor of Deer Park and Houston Mayor
Lee Brown, who will meet with company officials Thursday, spokesman
Don Payne said. The Houston Fire Department Hazardous Materials
team has also been notified.
</P>
<P>
   Despite the images of death and destruction that napalm evokes,
